data.description: Back on Market, no fault of the Property...  Charming 1220 sq ft home in the sought after Country Meadows of Temelec 55+ community! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch style home features vaulted ceilings and plenty of natural light in the living room. Kitchen has tile counters, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast area. The primary suite includes a large closet and full bathroom with walk-in shower. The second and third bedrooms can be used as an office and guest room. Additional features include an attached 2-car garage, a yard large enough for a beautiful garden and access to all of Country Meadow amenities pool, spa, and a great area for walking. This home is perfect for  relaxing retirement living! Conveniently located just minutes from shopping, dining, and major highways. Make this beautiful house your own - schedule a showing today! Virtual staging in some photos.  The roof is newer.  Disclosure IO link:  https://app.disclosures.io/link/1219-Herbazal-Street-dv7491mw
